snippet.title: The Fool Release Trailer
snippet.description:
A story driven 2D point and click about an unknowing character. Non is a mild manner new villager just moving into their own. They're excited to live a comfortable, peaceful life and get to know the other towns folk. 
Get the Game on Itch.io
https://kalalla.itch.io/upright-fool 

Developer: HoneyTrap Games
